00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:33.908
One thing that we would need is,

00:04:33.908 --> 00:04:36.827
we would need some
variation among the beetles.

00:04:36.827 --> 00:04:37.660
- [Voiceover] Okay.

00:04:37.660 --> 00:04:40.179
- [Voiceover] So, if you
have identical beetles,

00:04:40.179 --> 00:04:43.410
