different from each other.

00:04:55.045 --> 00:04:56.099
- [Voiceover] Awesome.

00:04:56.099 --> 00:04:59.080
You've made them different
colors, which is perfect.

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:00.663
We have variation,

00:05:00.663 --> 00:05:03.040
and the next ingredient
that we're going to need,

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:05.447
is we're gonna need that
variation to be heritable.

00:05:05.447 --> 00:05:07.304
We're gonna say that those beetles,

00:05:07.304 --> 00:05:10.113
